ygData.messageBody:
Fairy guards were blue to me at 30, the princess was white to me. On
Aqualungs you guys are selling them ALL WRONG!!!!! I have 15 orders at 1kpp
each for a 50 charge item, yes 1,000pp per lung. you need to make it seem
as though this is the most difficult thing in the world to make never sell
them directly either only take orders for them. I have so many level 50
druids who want them because they hate having to carry enough fish scales
for their party.

Efrieum
level 32 warrior
Innoruuk
